{"tid":1519706,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［正呀屌］民航處提醒公眾勿在機場附近放飛無人機及照射激光","createTime":"2019-08-30T15:40:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T22:46:25.000Z","uid":182994,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8ed89775b5cf7c3de6d326f85ff4814de6db3e0a","tid":1519706,"uid":182994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:40:05.000Z","msg":"民航處表示，留意到網上有人起星期日到機場表達訴求，包括在機場附近放飛無人機及照射激光，處方提醒公眾切勿在機場範圍及周邊地方做有關行為，以免觸犯法例及危害航空安全。<br />\n<br />\n民航處指，任何人如因魯莽或疏忽操作飛機而危害他人或財產安全，可被檢控，一經定罪，可處罰款及監禁兩年。根據機管局附例，違例放模型飛機，包括無人機，一經定罪，最高可判罰款五萬元及監禁六個月；至於以激光滋擾飛行，若被定罪可處罰款。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兩年對比起unlawful assembly 同暴動<br />\n簡直係蔗渣嘅價錢燒鵝嘅味道"},{"pid":"84effe9206e4bd5298c885540e004b9b72702ed3","tid":1519706,"uid":91721,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:42:20.000Z","msg":"我覺得，用蔗渣價錢燒鵝味道呢個比喻<br />\n有啲黑色幽默<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b69ea5baa17aaa9b1b0f81eae7d31f10d066a92","tid":1519706,"uid":169665,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:44:26.000Z","msg":"多謝民航處提醒，原來罰得咁輕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ccd698a73783e25b4641aba90d65872339051a1","tid":1519706,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:44:54.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n